=== EXAMPLE: scdoc_Classes_LorenzL_ex2 ===

DESCRIPTION: A neutral mixed sound, with saw_like oscillator character around 54 Hz, featuring very_slow attack and percussive envelope, with chaotic spectral movement, filtered with steep_rolloff character, and spectrally dense.

CATEGORIES:
  attack_time: very_slow
  brightness: neutral
  crest_factor_db: percussive
  envelope_flatness: flat
  harmonic_to_noise_ratio: mixed
  spectral_complexity_mean: dense
  spectral_flux_normalized: chaotic
  spectral_slope: steep_rolloff
  temporal_centroid: balanced

SYNTHESIS CONCEPTS (key values):
[oscillator]
  fundamental_freq: 53.8991
  harmonic_decay_rate: 0.3543
  harmonic_regularity: 0.9291
  pitch_clarity: 10.8948
  inharmonicity: 0.0416
  type: saw_like
[filter]
  spectral_slope: -38.5902
  resonance_freq: 0.0000

SUPERCOLLIDER CODE:
